Kristin Cavallari and her Chicago Bears fiance Jay Cutler tied the knot during an intimate ceremony at Woodmont Christian Church in Nashville, Tenn., on June 8, 2013. The couple, who welcomed baby boy Camden together in August 2012, were married in front of a small group of friends and family. Cavallari, 26, donned a stunning strapless Monique Lhuillier dress for the occasion along with a billowing veil and carried white peonies. The two had been engaged since November 2011.
